{
  "stem": "166.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this was only a short time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I worked there Saturday, there wasn't really too much work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He got me to clean his bicycle, and he gave me a pot of soup.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, go wash that pot out, especially because he knew I didn't have any food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Later on one day, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they came and they took the whole camp to the concentration camp, to Blechhammer.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In that camp, one guy ran away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One guy didn't come back, because when we went out from the camp to the work, and came back in the camp, they counted us-- how many.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was one short.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the whole group-- we were there, 50 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The whole group had to go into the barrack, and we got 25 on our ass.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were so brutal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The 25 on the ass-- you had to kneel on a little school, and bend over on a chair, and drop your pants.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was one guy with a whip on this side, and the other guy on the other side, and they whipped you so hard that every time they whipped force on you behind, there was right a black-blue stripe on it that you-- they had to carry you out.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was an incident that the father had to whip his son.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he didn't whip him hard, so the German comes over there and says, come here, lay down here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm going to show you how to whip.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he got him real, real hard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if you're not going to do this, you're going to get it more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] That's what it was, well, later on.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
